  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package is assigned Model Risk Level 5 due to high model influence and direct regulatory decision consequence with no physical testing backup. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed without documented justification, materially weakening the overall credibility evidence.",
